        {
            "id": 6424413,
            "title": "盤中速報 - DoorDash公司(DASH-US)大漲5.07%，報188.43美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>DoorDash公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DASH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DASH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DASH-US</a>)截至台北時間17日21:44股價上漲9.1美元，報188.43美元，漲幅5.07%，成交量475,383（股），盤中最高價188.44美元、最低價183.48美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.16%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.77%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.3%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>DoorDash公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DASH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DASH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DASH-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+16.03%</li> <li>近 1 月：+6.88%</li> <li>近 3 月：-12.66%</li> <li>近 6 月：-32.75%</li> <li>今年以來：-20.82%</li></ul></section></main>",
